<P>
   G8-CLINTON _ Okinawa _ The Group of Seven industrialized
nations, plus Russia, holds a three-day summit meeting to discuss
everything from U.S. plans for a national missile defense (NMD)
system to increased trade to Third World debt. Developing. (Chao,
