<SLUG> BC-OBIT-WERNER-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
RUTH WERNER, 93, COLORFUL AND DARING SOVIET SPY 
</HEADLINE>
  
 repeating to add art note (ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Nonsubscribers
can purchase one-time rights by calling 888-603-1036 or
888-346-9867.) 
 By DAVID BINDER   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
