</P>
<P>
   (Perennial/HarperCollins, $13.) How a murderer and
</P>
<P>
   certified lunatic helped James Murray complete the
</P>
<P>
   Oxford English Dictionary.
</P>
<P>
   15.(x) GUNS, GERMS AND STEEL, by Jared Diamond. (Norton,
</P>
<P>
   $14.95.) A physiologist attributes Western dominance
</P>
<P>
   to geography. (b)
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ADVICE, HOW-TO AND MISCELLANEOUS &LR;
</P>
